reviews.review_text:
Throwin' Stones.

Play it loud.

Hear yourself sing.

Nice later GD The first set AUD recording is a bit on the boomy side.  Second set is crystal clear.  Well played show throughout, the PITB sandwich is a highlight, along with the unexpected shift from SOTM to Wharf Rat.  Jerry gets a bit hoarse in the second set, but still a spirited evening worth a listen.
